Uses of Package
meico.mei

  • Packages that use meico.mei 
    Package Description
    meico.mei
    Contains the MEI class and a Helper class that is mostly used for MEI processing but offers some useful functionality also for other datatypes such as MSM and MPM.
    meico.musicxml
    Contains classes to interface MusicXML data.
  • Classes in meico.mei used by meico.mei 
    Class and Description
    ElementsByReferenceIds.ElementWithReferences
    This class represents an element and the reference IDs to other elements that it has in its attributes.
    ElementsByReferenceIds.ElementWithReferences.AttributesByReferenceId
    This class is a HashMap with all references that the provided element has and a list of the attributes where each reference is the value.
    Helper
    This class is used for mei to msm conversion to hold temporary data, used in class Mei.
    Mei
    This class holds the mei data from a source file in a XOM Document.
    Mei2MusicXmlConverter.DefinitionType
    Class to hold Information from definitions for a corresponding part.
  • Classes in meico.mei used by meico.musicxml 
    Class and Description
    Mei
    This class holds the mei data from a source file in a XOM Document.
